k=7
n=rep(0,k)
VY=rep(0,4)
VX=rep(0,4)
CXY=rep(0,4)
A=rep(0,4)
B=rep(0,4)
C=rep(0,4)
beta_hat=rep(0,k)
z=rep(0,k)
    for(i in 1:k)
      {
            n[i]=length(y[i,])
            VY[i]=var(y[i,])
         VX[i]=var(x[i,])
        CXY[i]=cov(x[i,],y[i,])
            A[i]=n[i]*VX[i]
            B[i]=n[i]*CXY[i]
            C[i]=n[i]*VY[i]
            beta_hat[i]=B[i]/A[i]
            z[i]=beta_hat[i]*B[i]
          }
      
CT=sum(C)
AT=sum(A)
BT=sum(B)
beta_hat_pooled=BT/AT
F_statistic=((CT-BT*beta_hat_pooled)-(CT-sum(z)))/(CT-sum(z))*((sum(n)-2*k)/(k-1))
